<p><strong>4. Student</strong></p>
<table>
<tr><th>Column</th><th>Type</th><th>Constraints</th><th>Description</th></tr>
<tr><td>StudentID</td><td>int</td><td>PK, Identity</td><td>Auto-increment primary key</td></tr>
<tr><td>UserID</td><td>int</td><td>FK &rarr; User.UserID, Unique</td><td>Link to authentication identity</td></tr>
<tr><td>MRN</td><td>nvarchar(20)</td><td>Unique, Not Null</td><td>University registration number</td></tr>
<tr><td>Name</td><td>nvarchar(200)</td><td>Not Null</td><td>Student full name</td></tr>
<tr><td>DOB</td><td>date</td><td>Not Null</td><td>Date of birth</td></tr>
<tr><td>Gender</td><td>nvarchar(10)</td><td>Nullable</td><td>Male &verbar; Female &verbar; Other &verbar; Prefer not to say</td></tr>
<tr><td>ContactInfoJSON</td><td>nvarchar(max)</td><td>Nullable</td><td>JSON: {email, phone, address, guardian}</td></tr>
<tr><td>EnrollmentStatus</td><td>nvarchar(20)</td><td>Not Null, Default: 'Active', Enum: <code>StudentLifecycleStatus</code></td><td>Active &verbar; OnLeave &verbar; Graduated &verbar; Expelled</td></tr>
<tr><td>ProgramID</td><td>int</td><td>FK &rarr; Program.ProgramID</td><td>Enrolled degree program</td></tr>
<tr><td>EntryTerm</td><td>nvarchar(20)</td><td>Not Null</td><td>e.g., Fall 2026</td></tr>
<tr><td>ExpectedGraduationTerm</td><td>nvarchar(20)</td><td>Nullable</td><td>Projected graduation term</td></tr>
<tr><td>CreatedAt</td><td>datetime2</td><td>Default: GETUTCDATE()</td><td>Record creation timestamp</td></tr>
</table>
<blockquote><strong>v10.1 Change:</strong> <code>EnrollmentStatus</code> enum values updated to Active &verbar; OnLeave &verbar; Graduated &verbar; Expelled (was Active &verbar; Graduated &verbar; Withdrawn &verbar; Suspended).</blockquote>

<p><strong>5. Transcript</strong></p>
<table>
<tr><th>Column</th><th>Type</th><th>Constraints</th><th>Description</th></tr>
<tr><td>TranscriptID</td><td>int</td><td>PK, Identity</td><td>Auto-increment primary key</td></tr>
<tr><td>StudentID</td><td>int</td><td>FK &rarr; Student.StudentID</td><td>Student whose transcript this is</td></tr>
<tr><td>IssuedAt</td><td>datetime2</td><td>Default: GETUTCDATE()</td><td>When the transcript was generated</td></tr>
<tr><td>EntriesJSON</td><td>nvarchar(max)</td><td>Not Null</td><td>JSON: [{courseCode, courseName, credits, grade, term}]</td></tr>
<tr><td>GPA</td><td>decimal(3,2)</td><td>Nullable</td><td>Cumulative GPA at time of issue</td></tr>
<tr><td>Status</td><td>nvarchar(20)</td><td>Not Null, Default: 'Draft', Enum: <code>TranscriptStatus</code></td><td>Draft &verbar; Issued &verbar; Revoked</td></tr>
<tr><td>TranscriptURI</td><td>nvarchar(500)</td><td>Nullable</td><td>Generated PDF URI in blob storage</td></tr>
</table>

<h3>Module 3: Course Catalog &amp; Curriculum (LMSService)</h3>

<p><strong>6. Course</strong></p>
<table>
<tr><th>Column</th><th>Type</th><th>Constraints</th><th>Description</th></tr>
